treeBuilder.newTree uses wd.PrettyString(), while the test uses wd.String(). If
these are different, the test will fail.

One difference is that `PrettyString()` uses `~/` for the home directory, while
`String()` returns the realpath.

The test failure may be triggered by setting GOTMPDIR.
